data.description:
AMAZING OPPORTUNITY FOR BRAND NEW HOME RENTAL! This beautiful new home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and modern amenities throughout. Open concept family room is perfect for gathering with friends and family providing a seamless dining and entertaining experience. Energy-efficient features and appliances are proven to drive utility costs down. The front doors of the elementary school can be seen from the front yard of the property making it perfect for a family with small children. One dog is allowed with weight and breed restrictions. A non-refundable pet deposit will be required before moving in.

24 Month Lease, $1,650 deposit, Available Now! No smoking, Small dogs allowed with non-refundable deposit. Contact us for more information.
